cat << EOF
GNU Gadu is an Instant Messenger program created to work with protocols
popular in Poland (but not only). This program is based on extensible plug-in
idea, also graphical user interface (written in GTK+) is a plugin. It 
supports Gadu-Gadu, Tlen.pl and Jabber protocols currently.
EOF
